review: First time I have been to dentist in over 30 years, was very  nervous. But as soon as I walked in the receptionists put me at ease. Then was called. Dr. Prabhu Dev explained all he was doing and was very gentle. only thing I felt was the needle in my roof of mouth. Not as bad as I thought. Did not feel tooth pain as it was very smooth, since the equipment's are high end. Doctor was very Kind and calm. What more could you need from a dentist? The staff are so kind, caring and thoughtful. They are really considerate of you, if you happen to be rather apprehensive. Thank you everyone at the clinic.
reply_text: Thank you for your kind words...
